divs: Sighting DetailsI did,t have my glasses on but could normally that a plane was a plane if it flew by. What I saw was shaped like a plane but VERY blurry as if it was a cloud. Didn't want to lose track of it trying to find my glasses. It travel the speed of a normal plane but with all the squinting I did, I couldn't make it out. It was traveling due south over the 11203 zip code. One thing I know for sure is that it wasn't a rouge cloud.
